name: 穆斯塔法·J·斯莱克
name_full: 穆斯塔法·J·斯莱克 Mustapha J. Slack
introduction: Mustapha J. Slack is an actor from Atlanta, Georgia. He found a passion for acting when he was 18 years old, after which he attended college with a focus in theatre. He received a Bachelor of Fine Arts in Theatre Performance from Columbus State University in 2017. He has studied further since then while also acting in various films, plays, television shows, and commercials in the southeast area.
